OL,3,CMan guilty after trying to smuggle 193
OL,4,Ckilos of cocaine in banana shipment
OL,6,FThe ringleader of a gang has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty after attempting to
OL,8,Fsmuggle 139 kilos of cocaine into the
OL,9,FUK, hidden in a consignment of bananas.
OL,11,FSajid Ali, 56, from Birmingham, was
OL,12,Farrested by the National Crime Agency
OL,13,Fat Heathrow Airport in January this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FHe was just minutes before boarding a
OL,17,Fflight to Istanbul, Turkey, where he
OL,18,Fwas living at the time.
