OL,6,FAli's associates had previously been
OL,7,Farrested while uploading a shipping
OL,8,Fcontainer they believed contained #11
OL,9,Fmillion pounds worth of drugs at a
OL,10,Fstorage company in Coventry.
OL,12,FThe rest of Ali's associates are
OL,13,Fserving a total of 62 years in prison.
OL,15,FAli had distanced himself from the
OL,16,Foperation, and instructed members of a
OL,17,Fcrime group via WhatsApp voice and
OL,18,Ftext messages.
