OL,3,CMan guilty after trying to smuggle 193
OL,4,Ckilos of cocaine in banana shipment
OL,6,FBall and Shahu travelled to Coventry,
OL,7,Fwhere the containers were being held,
OL,8,Fand tore open the roof with a crowbar.
OL,9,FBut as they did so, NCA and police
OL,10,Fofficers arrested them.
OL,12,FBall, Shahu and two associates:
OL,13,FFlorjan Ibra and Arman Kaviani were
OL,14,Fall arrested and jailed for a total of
OL,15,F62 years at Warwick Crown Court in
OL,16,FNovember last year.
OL,18,FAli was convicted by a jury on the
OL,19,F30th July at Coventry Crown Court and
OL,20,Fwill be sentenced on the 16th October.
