OL,4,Ckilos of cocaine in banana shipment
OL,6,FNCA Operations Manager Paul Orchard
OL,7,Fsaid: "There is no doubt that Sajid
OL,8,FAli pulled the strings for this group,
OL,9,Femploying Ball and Shahu to oversee
OL,10,Fthe dirty work of extracting what he
OL,11,Fthought were packages of cocaine from
OL,12,Fthe shipping container.
OL,14,F"Had this load not been intercepted
OL,15,Fand seized, it would have been worth
OL,16,Fmillions of pounds on the streets of
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,F"Ali was in this for profit, but this
OL,20,Fcriminality also comes at a huge human
OL,21,Fcost.
