OL,6,F"Cocaine fuels violence and
OL,7,Fexploitation, including gang culture
OL,8,Fand firearm and knife crime in the UK
OL,9,Fand around the world.
OL,11,FCaroline Hughes, Specialist Prosecutor
OL,12,Fin the CPS, said: "This was a major
OL,13,Foperation, which saw a vast quantity
OL,14,Fof drugs seized before they could
OL,15,Freach the community's streets.
