OL,3,CMan guilty after trying to smuggle 193
OL,4,Ckilos of cocaine in banana shipment
OL,6,F"Throughout the investigation, Sajid
OL,7,FAli refused to admit his involvement
OL,8,Fin this large-scale drug operation,
OL,9,Fhowever the evidence carefully pieced
OL,10,Ftogether by the NCA and the CPS
OL,11,Fdemonstrated the leading role he
OL,12,Fplayed in this importation.
OL,14,F"The CPS is committed to working with
OL,15,Finvestigators such as the National
OL,16,FCrime Agency to ensure that criminal
OL,17,Fdrugs gangs are brought to justice."
